snippet.title: Amber Heard's Friend Just Testified AGAINST HER!
snippet.description:
►Amber Heard's Friend Just Testified AGAINST HER! 
Not all love stories have happy endings. So was the case with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. They had met on the set of The Rum Diary, People magazine reported that Depp and Heard were engaged after a picture emerged of the actress wearing an ornate engagement ring, which was later confirmed by Johnny Depp in a video interview with the Daily Mail. They married in 2015 in a private ceremony.
